ID: unicorn
TITLE: Unicorn

===

Over a blotter a field of never-ending wonder
Inside my echoed mind I see things quick and fast

Cause of the unicorn

The speed outside my brain was too far gone inside me
I tried to catch it, but it took me for a ride

Cause of the unicorn

Although my head feels like a jar of melted jello
I still see everything as if it were a blur

Cause of the unicorn
